### DOCKER NGINX + SSL

first create on your local folder the certificate through a docker volume of nginx image::
```
docker run -v /Users/pierangeloorizio/Desktop/certificate:/work -it nginx openssl req -x509 -nodes -days 365 -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout /work/nginx.key -out /work/nginx.crt
```

```
docker run --name docker-nginx -p 80:80 -p 8081:443 -v /Users/pierangeloorizio/Desktop/nginx-test/default.conf:/etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf -v /Users/pierangeloorizio/Desktop/nginx-test/certificate:/etc/nginx/ssl/ -d nginx
```
